00:52:02.260 --> 00:52:08.150
umm, and through a number of other, uh, schools
of philosophy, Confucius lost

00:52:08.150 --> 00:52:12.840
his mother -- or father when he was three;
Abraham Lincoln lost his mother when

00:52:12.840 --> 00:52:17.230
he was nine. In other words, these are -- and
a number of founders of

00:52:17.230 --> 00:52:21.000
philosophy were raised in what we would call
single-parent homes now. So

00:52:21.000 --> 00:52:26.910
